intent.user_query: what are my top 5 customers based on revenue generated?

phases.goal: Calculate the revenue generated by each customer.

key_arguments.sql: SELECT c.CustomerID, c.FirstName, c.LastName, SUM(s.TotalAmount) AS TotalRevenue FROM fitness_db.Customers c JOIN fitness_db.Sales s ON c.CustomerID = s.CustomerID GROUP BY c.CustomerID, c.FirstName, c.LastName

phases.goal: Generate the final report based on the data gathered.
